const randomString = utils.generateRandomString();
const header = [
    "key1",
    "key2",
    "validTo",
    "validFrom",
    "conditionValue",
    "priceUnit",
    "unitOfMeasure",
    "currency",
    "attribute1",
    "attribute3"
];
const data = [
    [
        "A1",
        randomString,
        "9999-12-31",
        "2025-01-01",
        10,
        1,
        "PC",
        "USD",
        "A",
        "B"
    ],
    [
        "A2",
        randomString,
        "9999-12-31",
        "2025-01-01",
        10,
        1,
        "PC",
        "USD",
        "A",
        "B"
    ]
];
cy.validateBulkloadRequestSchema(header, data, 'validFrom', 'CONDITION_RECORD_STAGING');
